  "detailed_description": "Setia is suddenly attacked while napping, and her precious magic crystal is stolen by unknown enemies.<br>Will she be able to retrieve her stolen crystal?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453530/extras/38f39a5851c83c7d507cba0972ed7d8a.apng?t=1743670243\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453530/extras/38f39a5851c83c7d507cba0972ed7d8a.poster.avif?t=1743670243\" class=\"bb_img\" width=550 height=324 /></picture></span><br>White Blade is a short turn-based strategy game, where players strategically consider the unique skills of both their own characters and enemies in order to defeat their opponents.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453530/extras/ed93fc1475ac9d3a49457804c5ed1306.poster.avif?t=1743670243\" width=550 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453530/extras/ed93fc1475ac9d3a49457804c5ed1306.webm?t=1743670243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> New skills that are added as the game progresses<br></li><li> Unique finishing strike illustrations for each skill<br></li><li> Various hints provided when the player is unable to progress<br></li><li> Special skills that enemies use only at the highest difficulty<br></li><li> 'Special Effect Combo' option that allows players to directly modify the combat system<br></li><li> Plus other features</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453530/extras/f4116ef2de60b817aeecfa227fc0d511.avif?t=1743670243\" width=616 height=200 /></span>",
